1. *Planina* je prekrivena snegom. (The *mountain* is covered in snow.)
2. Kada sam bio mali, obožavao sam da penjem po *planinama*. (When I was young, I loved climbing *mountains*.)
3. Želimo da posetimo sve najviše *planine* u Srbiji. (We want to visit all the highest *mountains* in Serbia.)
4. Udaljenost između dve *planine* je deset kilometara. (The distance between two *mountains* is ten kilometers.)
5. Često idem na trčanje na *planinu* iza moje kuće. (I often go for a run on the *mountain* behind my house.)
6. Naš plan je da se popnemo na vrh te *planine*. (Our plan is to climb to the top of that *mountain*.)
7. *Planine* u Srbiji su prekrasnog izgleda. (The *mountains* in Serbia have a beautiful appearance.)
8. Danas smo videli mnogo divljih životinja na toj *planini*. (Today we saw many wild animals on that *mountain*.)
9. Nisam siguran kako se zove ta *planina* na horizontu. (I'm not sure what that *mountain* on the horizon is called.)
10. Naša kuća se nalazi na padinama jedne od najlepših *planina* u Srbiji. (Our house is located on the slopes of one of the most beautiful *mountains* in Serbia.)